Name
       timing_enable_zero_delay_analysis_mode

Syntax
       timing_enable_zero_delay_analysis_mode

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true,  the  software  will use zero delays during timing
       analysis.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

